| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2672 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 17159d0c-17bc-5737-9fb7-06d5aca1b8e5"
